{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"From all outward appearances,"},{"time":3000,"text":"John had everything going for him."},{"time":6000,"text":"He had just signed the contract"},{"time":8000,"text":"to sell his New York apartment"},{"time":10000,"text":"at a six-figure profit,"},{"time":12000,"text":"and he'd only owned it for five years."},{"time":15000,"text":"The school where he graduated from with his master's"},{"time":17000,"text":"had just offered him a teaching appointment,"},{"time":19000,"text":"which meant not only a salary,"},{"time":21000,"text":"but benefits for the first time in ages."},{"time":25000,"text":"And yet, despite everything going really well for John,"},{"time":28000,"text":"he was struggling,"},{"time":30000,"text":"fighting addiction and a gripping depression."}]},{"cues":[{"time":35000,"text":"On the night of June 11th, 2003,"},{"time":37000,"text":"he climbed up to the edge"},{"time":39000,"text":"of the fence on the Manhattan Bridge"},{"time":42000,"text":"and he leaped to the treacherous waters below."},{"time":47000,"text":"Remarkably --"},{"time":49000,"text":"no, miraculously --"},{"time":51000,"text":"he lived."},{"time":54000,"text":"The fall shattered his right arm,"},{"time":57000,"text":"broke every rib that he had,"},{"time":59000,"text":"punctured his lung,"},{"time":61000,"text":"and he drifted in and out of consciousness"},{"time":63000,"text":"as he drifted down the East River,"},{"time":66000,"text":"under the Brooklyn Bridge"},{"time":68000,"text":"and out into the pathway of the Staten Island Ferry,"},{"time":71000,"text":"where passengers on the ferry"},{"time":73000,"text":"heard his cries of pain,"},{"time":75000,"text":"contacted the boat's captain"},{"time":77000,"text":"who contacted the Coast Guard"},{"time":79000,"text":"who fished him out of the East River"},{"time":81000,"text":"and took him to Bellevue Hospital."}]},{"cues":[{"time":84000,"text":"And that's actually where our story begins."},{"time":87000,"text":"Because once John committed himself"},{"time":89000,"text":"to putting his life back together --"},{"time":92000,"text":"first physically, then emotionally,"},{"time":95000,"text":"and then spiritually --"},{"time":97000,"text":"he found that there were very few resources available"},{"time":100000,"text":"to someone who has attempted to end their life"},{"time":102000,"text":"in the way that he did."}]},{"cues":[{"time":105000,"text":"Research shows"},{"time":107000,"text":"that 19 out of 20 people"},{"time":109000,"text":"who attempt suicide"},{"time":111000,"text":"will fail."},{"time":114000,"text":"But the people who fail"},{"time":116000,"text":"are 37 times more likely to succeed"},{"time":119000,"text":"the second time."},{"time":122000,"text":"This truly is"},{"time":124000,"text":"an at-risk population"},{"time":126000,"text":"with very few resources to support them."},{"time":129000,"text":"And what happens"},{"time":131000,"text":"when people try to assemble themselves back into life,"},{"time":134000,"text":"because of our taboos around suicide,"},{"time":136000,"text":"we're not sure what to say,"},{"time":138000,"text":"and so quite often we say nothing."},{"time":141000,"text":"And that furthers the isolation"},{"time":143000,"text":"that people like John found themselves in."}]},{"cues":[{"time":148000,"text":"I know John's story very well"},{"time":150000,"text":"because I'm John."},{"time":154000,"text":"And this is, today,"},{"time":157000,"text":"the first time in any sort of public setting"},{"time":160000,"text":"I've ever acknowledged"},{"time":162000,"text":"the journey that I have been on."},{"time":166000,"text":"But after having lost a beloved teacher in 2006"},{"time":169000,"text":"and a good friend last year to suicide,"},{"time":173000,"text":"and sitting last year at TEDActive,"},{"time":176000,"text":"I knew that I needed to step out of my silence"},{"time":179000,"text":"and past my taboos"},{"time":181000,"text":"to talk about an idea worth spreading --"},{"time":184000,"text":"and that is that people"},{"time":186000,"text":"who have made the difficult choice"},{"time":189000,"text":"to come back to life"},{"time":191000,"text":"need more resources and need our help."}]},{"cues":[{"time":195000,"text":"As the Trevor Project says, it gets better."},{"time":198000,"text":"It gets way better."},{"time":201000,"text":"And I'm choosing to come out"},{"time":203000,"text":"of a totally different kind of closet today"},{"time":205000,"text":"to encourage you, to urge you,"},{"time":208000,"text":"that if you are someone"},{"time":210000,"text":"who has contemplated or attempted suicide,"},{"time":214000,"text":"or you know somebody who has,"},{"time":217000,"text":"talk about it; get help."},{"time":220000,"text":"It's a conversation worth having"},{"time":223000,"text":"and an idea worth spreading."}]},{"cues":[{"time":226000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":228000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}